const ArrowLeftIcon = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      fill="#3f568d"
      width="24"
      height="24"
      style={{
        position: "fixed",
        top: "10px",
        left: "10px",
        zIndex: "9999",
      }}
    >
      <g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" strokeWidth="0"></g>
      <g
        id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier"
        strokeLinecap="round"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
      ></g>
      <g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier">
        <title></title>
        <g id="Complete">
          <g id="arrow-left">
            <g>
              <polyline
                data-name="Right"
                fill="none"
                id="Right-2"
                points="7.6 7 2.5 12 7.6 17"
                stroke="#000000"
                strokeLinecap="round"
                strokeLinejoin="round"
                strokeWidth="2"
              ></polyline>
              <line
                fill="none"
                stroke="#000000"
                strokeLinecap="round"
                strokeLinejoin="round"
                strokeWidth="2"
                x1="21.5"
                x2="4.8"
                y1="12"
                y2="12"
              ></line>
            </g>
          </g>
          <text
            x="8"
            y="13"
            fill="black"
            style={{
              fontSize: "12px",
              fontWeight: "bold",
              transform: "translate(15px, 0)",
            }}
          >
            Back
          </text>
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default ArrowLeftIcon;
